v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a g\u1ea7n 100 ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou. C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Barca v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a v\u01a1i n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n thua AS Roma 0-3 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n s\u1edbm h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung diem nhan sau tran dau Barca vs Valencia vong 32 La Liga hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/Nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-dau-Barca-vs-Valencia-vong-32-La-Liga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi Valencia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 chung c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 ch\u00fat u\u1ec3 o\u1ea3i khi nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Valencia l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt. Th\u1eadt may l\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Barca kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u1eadt kh\u1edfi, th\u1eafng 2-1 \u0111i k\u00e8m 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Valencia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ee9ng trong t\u1ed1p 4</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 sa s\u00fat l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n, s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean c\u1ee7a Valencia m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t trong th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 kh\u00f4n ngoan, B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Simone Zaza, Neto, Jeison Murillo, Geoffrey Kondogbia hay Goncalo Guedes&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Marcelino c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Valencia &ldquo;thay da, \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1ecbt&rdquo;. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mong manh trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi v\u00ed d\u1ee5 r\u00f5 n\u00e9t l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n thua sau 5 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi 60 b\u00e0n sau 32 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m Barcelona v\u00e0 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barcelona vs Valencia Coutinho di bong\" title=\"Barcelona vs Valencia Coutinho di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/barca-21-valencia-nhung-mien-cam-xuc-lan-lon-vi-coutinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Valencia ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Valencia t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 7. H\u1ecd si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong vi\u1ec7c tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ter Stegen, nh\u1eefng Rodrigo hay Guedes \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 1 cho Valencia. R\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Dani Parejo v\u1eabn l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb x\u1ee9 Castellon c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Valencia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 15 v\u00e0 51 v\u1edbi 1 t\u1eeb c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Suarez, 1 t\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Umtiti. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Marcelino tr\u1eafng tay r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Barca d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-barca-vs-valencia-21h15-ngay-144-la-liga-201718-372-184239.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/ket-qua-barca-vs-valencia-tran-dau-vong-32-la-liga-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-barca-vs-valencia-21h15-ngay-144-la-liga-201718-372-184239.html\">Barca 2-1 Valencia (KT): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i La Liga sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ee7i h\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma \u1edf Champions League, Barca c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n cho 2 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nCoutinho ch\u1ee9ng minh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Liverpool v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 160 tri\u1ec7u Euro, Philippe Coutinho \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u1eeb l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c b\u1edfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng tr\u00f4i qua, Coutinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i l\u00ean tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Anh d\u1ea7n t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barcelona thang Valencia 2-1\" title=\"Barcelona thang Valencia 2-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-dau-barca-vs-valencia-vong-32-la-liga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng Coutinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Barca ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Valencia \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Coutinho. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh ch\u1ecdc khe lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t r\u1eebng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng gi\u00fap Suarez \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Neto m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Coutinho \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c gi\u00fap Umtiti \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Coutinho c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca. Anh gi\u00fap li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn, cung c\u1ea5p \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong ng\u00e0y Messi b\u1ecb theo k\u00e8m s\u00e1t sao. Nh\u00ecn Coutinho t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, C\u0110V Barca h\u1eb3n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc khi anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd d\u1ef1 Champions League v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma h\u1ed3i gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-vs-valencia-180-184271.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-vs-valencia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-vs-valencia-180-184271.html\">HLV Valverde b\u00e0ng quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca</span><br>\r\n<span>Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Valencia 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadp n\u00ean m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i La Liga. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Barca vs Valencia l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y quan...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Valverde gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean t\u00e1c phong l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League, HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m. C\u1ef1u HLV Athletic Bilbao c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ebfn khi thua 0-3, Barca m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f9ng l\u00ean song qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn, Valverde b\u1ecb quy tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m cho vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Barca \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Messi t\u1ecf ra m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u00e0 hi\u1ebfm khi cho Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9. Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde\" title=\"HLV Valverde\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-vs-valencia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Valverde v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a thay \u0111\u1ed5i phong c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Nelson Semedo v\u00e0 Ivan Rakitic (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng), nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Coutinho v\u00e0 Paulinho, Valverde gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean 9 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Valencia nh\u01b0 khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Roma. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Barca trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng ch\u1edd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 Barca ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f4ng \u00edt s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Valencia. V\u1eabn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n, c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Coutinho v\u00e0 1 pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, Barca kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Valencia v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn. Qua \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi ng\u1edd d\u00e0nh cho HLV Valverde v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a d\u1ee9t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nBarcelona:</strong> Ter Stegen, Pique,Umtiti, Alba, Roberto, Busquets, Paulinho, Iniesta (D.Suarez 84'), Coutinho (Dembele 79'), L.Suarez, Messi.<br>\r\n<strong>Valencia: </strong>Neto, Garay, Vezo, Gabriel, Gaya, Guedes (Pereira 69'), Kondogbia, Pareno, Soler, Rodrigo (Zaza 80'), Mina (Vietto 71').<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Barca vs Valencia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Barca-vs-Valencia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca 2-1 Valencia (V\u00f2ng 32 La Liga 2017/18):</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/14/Highlight-Barca-vs-Valencia-vong-32-La-Liga.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-da-quen-di-that-bai-truoc-roma-180-184280.html\">&ldquo;Barca \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00ean \u0111i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-vs-valencia-180-184271.html\">HLV Valverde b\u00e0ng quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-barca-21-valencia