\u1ea5p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 18 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u01b0 duy x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong Man City mua De Ligt than dong Ha Lan hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City mua De Ligt th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng H\u00e0 Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/chuyen-nhuong-man-city-mua-de-ligt.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Ligt ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Ajax</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Man City \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng H\u00e0 Lan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, De Ligt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0110T H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3 n\u0103m 2017 khi m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n 17 tu\u1ed5i. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 hoa Tulip v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Barcelona, Man City mua De Ligt l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Mirror ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: De Ligt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cVirgil van Dijk m\u1edbi\u201d c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0 Lan trong khi Man City t\u1eebng vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Liverpool trong 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qua. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh Van Dijk.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Guardiola\" title=\"HLV Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-chuc-vo-dich-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man City mua De Ligt, ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p HLV\u00a0Guardiola</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, De Ligt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. S\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y t\u1eeb Man City mua De Ligt. T\u1ed1i nay, trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Ajax l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n PSV v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean t\u1edbi t\u1eeb N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a De Ligt v\u1edbi Ajax c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2021. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1999 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 15 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu sang Man City, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n nh\u1eadn g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-man-city-chi-600-trieu-bang-mua-sam-172-184154.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1edbn cho mua s\u1eafm nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</strong></span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-tinh-gay-soc-voi-mbappe-172-184298.html\">Man City t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Mbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-man-city-chi-600-trieu-bang-mua-sam-172-184154.html\">Man City chi \u201cti\u1ec1n t\u1ea5n\u201d v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-khong-thay-doi-ke-hoach-mua-sam-sau-tran-thua-liverpool-172-184096.html\">Man City kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/man-city-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-isco-176-183878.html\">Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 Isco</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tiet-lo-raiola-suyt-ban-pogba-sang-man-city-vao-mua-dong-172-183681.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Raiola su\u00fdt b\u00e1n Pogba sang Man City v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1216","checkdouble":"184311"},{"date":"15:37 15/04","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Newcastle vs Arsenal 19h30 ng\u00e0y 15/4 (Premier League 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/truc-tiep-newcastle-vs-arsenal-19h30-ngay-154-premier