 ch\u00ed Kane c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0a con g\u00e1i ra \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec1 th\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n &ldquo;s\u1ed1ng l\u1ed7i&rdquo; c\u1ee7a k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch, Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean, k\u00e8m \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1ec9a mai tr\u00ean Twitter. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Liverpool c\u1ee7a Salah c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng v\u1eeba, khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y Harry Kane.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Bournemouth v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mane, Salah v\u00e0 Firmino. H\u00f2a chung &quot;phong tr\u00e0o&quot; <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cong-dong-mang-thi-nhau-troll-viec-harry-kane-doi-ban-thang-172-184088.html\" target=\"_blank\">c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng tr\u00eau ch\u1ecdc Harry Kane</span>, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Henderson cho bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e1ng ra Salah ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f2i 2 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 hattrick. M\u1ed9t c\u00fa t\u00e1t th\u1eb3ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u01b0\u1ee3n Salah, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Liverpool ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\" title=\"Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-salah-sap-toi-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u01b0\u1ee3n Salah, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Liverpool ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u00e2ng, Salah n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo; &ndash; Henderson h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u. &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i. Salah r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n trong to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo; &ndash; Henderson n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, James Milner c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p vui, tr\u00eau ch\u1ecdc h\u00e0nh vi Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tr\u00ean Twitter sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mohamed Salah&hellip; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hattrick, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u1edfi 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f9a vui v\u1ebb, Henderson c\u0169ng ca ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane: &ldquo;B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd n\u00ean coi th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, Kane lu\u00f4n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Salah c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_266512\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/15/highlight-liverpool-vs-bournemouth-vong-34-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-bao-ve-hanh-dong-doi-ban-thang-cua-kane-172-184124.html\">Pochettino b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Kane</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cong-dong-mang-thi-nhau-troll-viec-harry-kane-doi-ban-thang-172-184088.html\">C\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng thi nhau troll vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/doi-lai-cong-bang-harry-kane-bi-doi-thu-salah-mia-mai-172-184083.html\">\u0110\u00f2i l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, Harry Kane b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Salah m\u1ec9a mai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-liverpool-30-bournemouth-172-184283.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n n\u1ed