u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Man City coi nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd \u0111em Premier League v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, b\u1edfi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1eefa s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng quang.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Man xanh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Man \u0111\u1ecf th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Brom v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 thua CLB \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ed5 b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Spurs, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft: \u201c\u1ed2 kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u1eb9n ch\u01a1i golf r\u1ed3i, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111i ch\u01a1i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, \u0111\u00e1nh golf v\u1edbi con trai c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuan bi vo dich Premier League, Pep khong dem xia den MU hinh anh\" title=\"Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, Pep kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/Chuan-bi-vo-dich-Premier-League,-Pep-khong-dem-xia-den-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh golf ch\u1ee9 Pep kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNg\u00e0y mai v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 3 ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i golf m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Man United s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d \u2013 HLV n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham, \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 sau 10-15 ph\u00fat b\u00f3ng l\u0103n. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i trong hi\u1ec7p 1 th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1eefa v\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u1eb3ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u00f4m nay hay ng\u00e0y mai, Man City s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh Premier League. Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t, sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua 1 tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho d\u00f9 Pep kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn MU, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mong cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u2026 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tu\u1ed9t kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Man City s\u1ebd \u0103n m\u1eebng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u. V\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Swansea, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng quang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn 2 CLB th\u00e0nh Manchester<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-chuc-vo-dich-nha-172-184309.html\">Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00f4ng \u00fd ngh\u0129a b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-pogba-va-phong-do-cua-anh-172-184310.html\">Mourinho ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-13-man-city-mot-buoc-toi-thien-duong-172-184282.html\">Tottenham 1-3 Man City: M\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/antonio-valencia-mu-se-thach-thuc-moi-danh-hieu-o-mua-giai-toi-172-184297.html\">Antonio Valencia: M.U s\u1ebd th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-vs-west-brom-22h00-ngay-154-tien-khach-ve-noi-xa-172-184266.html\">Man Utd vs West Brom (22h00 ng\u00e0y 15/4): Ti\u1ec5n kh\u00e1ch v\u1ec1 n\u01a1i xa</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1212","checkdouble":"184318"},{"date":"11:38 15/04","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus vs Sampdoria 23h00 ng\u00e0y 15/4 (Serie A 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/15/nhan-dinh-juventus-vs-sampdoria-23h00-ngay-154-serie-a-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a