div class='chitiet_tin'><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i 14/4, CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL thua CLB Sai Gon la vi bau Duc hinh anh\" title=\"HAGL thua CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u00ec b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/du-am-sai-gon-31-hagl-thanh-bai-o-hang-thu.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HAGL thua CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u00ec lo ng\u1ea1i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1ecf gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111ang g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Qua b\u00e1o ch\u00ed, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat dao \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u. BHL v\u1eabn tr\u1ea5n an c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t&rdquo;, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd cho HAGL r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span> n\u1ebfu b\u1ea7u T\u00fa n\u1eafm ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm 7 ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ki\u00eam T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VPF.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong><em>Highlight S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 3-1 HAGL (V\u00f2ng 5 V-League)</em></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/14/Highlight-Sai-Gon-vs-HAGL-vong-5-v-league.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: