 style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Newcastle vs Arsenal (19h30 ngay 1504) Dung dua voi Chich choe hinh anh\" title=\"Newcastle vs Arsenal (19h30 ng\u00e0y 1504) \u0110\u1eebng \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi Ch\u00edch ch\u00f2e h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Newcastle-vs-Arsenal-(19h30-ngay-1504)-Dung-dua-voi-Chich-choe-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, song Arsenal g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o Top 4. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, k\u00e9m Tottenham 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal san b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Atletico. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 d\u1ed3n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, Newcastle vs Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, song Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Newcastle vs Arsenal\" title=\"Preview Newcastle vs Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Preview-Newcastle-vs-Arsenal.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Newcastle vs Arsenal \u1edf v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Arsenal s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Santi Cazorla, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Granit Xhaka v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a David Ospina v\u00e0 Aaron Ramsey v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Arsenal. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Premier League, chu\u1ed7i th\u1eafng d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u1edbi 11 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Newcastle v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Newcastle kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Newcastle. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i &ldquo;Ch\u00edch ch\u00f2e&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leicester that bai truoc mot Newcastle co phong do tot\" title=\"Leicester th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Newcastle c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/tong-hop-leicester-12-newcastle-vong-33-premier-league-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Newcastle \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nArsenal kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 tr\u1eadn thua. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 thua t\u1edbi 8 sau 15 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u1edf Premier League. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Newcastle c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao. 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn 4 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn. \u1ede Premier League, &ldquo;Ch\u00edch ch\u00f2e&rdquo; th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng Arsenal, Newcastle s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y g\u1ea7n 4 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Newcastle tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong n\u0103m 2018. 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n St. Jame's Park th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Rafa Benitez b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u1ea1i Premier League, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u00fap Newcastle v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 10 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng khi b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i nh\u00f3m nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1 an to\u00e0n trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 v\u00f2ng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal thang tran thu 6 tren moi mat tran\" title=\"Arsenal th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/thay-gi-sau-chien-thang-day-kich-tinh-cua-arsenal-truoc-southampton.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Arsenal \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Newcastle</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nHLV Benitez c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Wenger. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 23 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi&nbsp;Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a Newcastle, Napoli, Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Valencia, trong chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn 57%.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau chuy\u1ebfn bay r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga th\u00ec Newcasle l\u1ea1i sung s\u1ee9c sau m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i St. Jame's Park kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Newcastle vs Arsenal, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf Premier League c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u. &ldquo;Ch\u00edch ch\u00f2e&rdquo; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3 th\u1eafng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u00ec h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Newcastle vs Arsenal\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Newcastle vs Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/Newcastle-vs-Arsenal-(4-4-1-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Newcastle vs Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 2-2</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1206","checkdouble":"184296"},{"date":"10:24 15/04","title":"Antonio Valencia: \"M.U s\u1ebd th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\